        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Focus on their recent comparable sales record, not their office brand or the price estimate they give you at appraisal. Ask how many properties they personally sold in your suburb and price bracket in the past six months, what the final prices were relative to initial price guidance, and how long those campaigns ran. An agent who can give you specific, honest answers to these questions is demonstrating the transparency they will show throughout your campaign."
      }
